properties.value: Bob shirts are a series of 5 differently coloured shirts depicting Bob the Jagex Cat. These shirts can be obtained from Easy Treasure Trails. When examined, they all read; "Bob says: '<sentence>'". The sentence is always a rule or advice for players from Jagex.

content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Bob shirt

Bob shirts are a series of 5 differently coloured shirts depicting Bob the Jagex Cat. These shirts can be obtained from Easy Treasure Trails. When examined, they all read; "Bob says: '<sentence>'". The sentence is always a rule or advice for players from Jagex.
